  question:
    sentences:
    - The alchemists are a bunch of strange people, albeit very knowledeable and contribute
      to the kingdom with many useful inventions. But the holy church is always in
      a fight with them. This time, the Pope accused them of heresy and is asking
      the royal court to judge and execute them. What will you do?
